title: #625 - Kate Quigley
description:
Kate Quigley, comedian, actress, and host of the "#DateFails" podcast, joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt LIVE in studio. 

See Joey and Kate LIVE at the New York Comedy Festival November 8-10 at Gotham Comedy Club.
